<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: CE: Ammo crafting -->
  <CE_AmmoCrafting.label>CE: 制造弹药</CE_AmmoCrafting.label>
  <!-- EN: Ensuring your colonists are supplied with quality ammo is vital to surviving on a Rimworld. Simple stone arrows can be obtained from the crafting but perform very poorly against opponents with advanced armor and clothing.\n\nSteel and plasteel arrows offer better penetration and can be made at the smithing bench once smithing is researched.\n\nResearch gunsmithing to unlock the loading bench, where you can craft ammo for most firearms. Artillery shells and grenades are made at the machining table.\n\nWhile most conventional ammo types can be made from simple raw materials, advanced ammo requires more exotic ingredients such as components, FSX or Prometheum. -->
  <CE_AmmoCrafting.helpText>确保殖民者使用高质量的弹药对于在边缘世界上生存至关重要。简单的石箭可以在手工制作点制作，但面对拥有先进盔甲和服装的敌人时表现非常糟糕。\n\n铁箭和玻璃钢箭有更好的穿透力，在研究锻造后可以在锻造台制造。\n\n研究枪械制作以解锁弹药装配台，来为大多数火器制造弹药。炮弹和手榴弹是在机械加工台上制造的。\n\n大多数常规弹药可以用简单的原材料制造，但先进弹药需要更特殊的材料如零部件、含胺乳化燃料或苯基液体燃料。</CE_AmmoCrafting.helpText>
  
  <!-- EN: CE: Fighting Mechanoids -->
  <CE_CentipedeArmor.label>CE: 对抗机械体</CE_CentipedeArmor.label>
  <!-- EN: Warning: It is only a matter of time before Mechanoids take notice of your arrival and start attacking. The larger models have heavy armor that is impervious to small-arms fire.\n\nFighting them requires powerful weapons such as heavy machine guns or explosives. You should keep a healthy stockpile of these weapons if you hope to survive for long. -->
  <CE_CentipedeArmor.helpText>警告：机械体注意到你并开始攻击只是时间问题。大型机械族覆盖着重装甲，不会被小型枪械穿透。\n\n与它们战斗需要强大的武器，如重机枪或爆炸物。如果你希望活得久一点，做好储备。 </CE_CentipedeArmor.helpText>
  
  <!-- EN: CE: Mass and bulk -->
  <CE_InventoryWeightBulk.label>CE: 质量和体积</CE_InventoryWeightBulk.label>
  <!-- EN: You can order your colonists to pick up items and store them in their inventory. They are limited in this by their carry weight and bulk capacity.\n\nCarry weight is determined by movement capacity and the more weight a colonist is carrying, the slower they are.\n\nBulk represents the space in your colonists' pockets and can be increased by equipping loadbearing gear like backpacks and tactical vests. The more stuffed their pockets are, the slower they'll work, so only pick up things you actually need.\n\nYou can check a colonist's load by selecting them, clicking the INVENTORY button and hovering over the displayed bars.\n\nTo order a colonist to pick something up, select him, right-click an item and select the 'Pick up' option. -->
  <CE_InventoryWeightBulk.helpText>你可以命令殖民者拿起物品并放在他们的物品栏中。存放会受到重量和体积携带能力的限制。\n\n质量携带能力由移动能力决定，并且殖民者携带的质量越多，速度就越慢。\n\n体积携带能力代表殖民者口袋中的空间，可以通过装备背包和战术背心等承重装备来增加。装的东西越多，工作越慢，所以最好只拿需要的东西。\n\n你可以选择殖民者，单击“库存”按钮，并将鼠标悬停在状态栏上来检查他的负荷。\n\n要命令殖民者拿起东西，请选择他，右键单击一个物品，然后选择“拿起”选项。</CE_InventoryWeightBulk.helpText>
  
  <!-- EN: CE: Loadouts -->
  <CE_Loadouts.label>CE: 携带方针</CE_Loadouts.label>
  <!-- EN: Colonists can be told to automatically pick up certain items to avoid inventory micromanagement. For example you can tell them to keep ammo for their primary weapon and they will stock up after a firefight.\n\nOpen the ASSIGN tab and press the 'Manage loadouts' button. Create a new loadout and set the items and quantity you want your colonists to keep. Then you can assign that loadout to your colonists and they will automatically manage their inventories. -->
  <CE_Loadouts.helpText>你可以告诉殖民者自动拾取某些物品，来减少微操。比如你可以让他们保持主要武器的弹药量，他们将在交火后自动取弹药。\n\n打开“方案”选项卡，然后按“管理携带方针”按钮。创建一个新的携带方针并设置需要持有的东西和数量。然后就可以把携带方针分配给你的殖民者，他们会自动管理他们的库存。</CE_Loadouts.helpText>
  
  <!-- EN: CE: Obtaining FSX -->
  <CE_ObtainingFSX.label>CE: 获取含胺乳化燃料</CE_ObtainingFSX.label>
  <!-- EN: FSX is the main ingredient for explosives such as frag grenades and mortar shells. You can obtain it either through traders or by taming boomrats and boomalopes, then harvesting the volatile chemicals they produce.\n\nOnce tamed they will produce a steady stream of FSX that your colonists will automatically harvest similar to other animal resources like wool and milk.\n\nYou can see your animal's current chemical fullness by selecting it and checking the readout in the lower-left corner. -->
  <CE_ObtainingFSX.helpText>含胺乳化燃料是爆炸物的主要成分，如烟雾手榴弹和迫击炮弹。你可以在商人处购买或者驯服爆炸鼠或爆炸羊，然后采集它们产生的挥发性化学物质。\n\n驯服后，它们会稳定的生产含胺乳化炸药，殖民者会自动采集含胺乳化炸药，类似于其他动物资源(如羊毛和牛奶)。\n\n选取动物并检查左下角的读数，可以看到动物当前的生产进度。</CE_ObtainingFSX.helpText>
  
  <!-- EN: CE: Obtaining Prometheum -->
  <CE_ObtainingPrometheum.label>CE: 获取苯基液体燃料</CE_ObtainingPrometheum.label>
  <!-- EN: Prometheum is used in most incendiary weapons such as incendiary mortar shells, AP-I rounds and molotovs. It is a highly flammable liquid that is harvested from the blazebulb plant.\n\nTo grow blazebulb, simply select a growing zone and set it to plant blazebulb.\n\nWarning: Blazebulbs are highly sensitive and have a chance to ignite if the surrounding temperature exceeds 28°C/82F. They will also leak puddles of Prometheum when damaged, which ignite on contact with air.\n\nMake sure your plantation has good climate control and is fire-proofed, otherwise it might quickly turn into a blazing inferno! -->
  <CE_ObtainingPrometheum.helpText>苯基液体燃料被用于大多数燃烧武器，如迫击炮燃烧弹、穿甲燃烧弹和莫洛托夫燃烧弹。它是高度易燃的液体，可以从叫做焰球罂粟的植物中提取。\n\n要种植焰球罂粟，只需选择一个种植区域，并将目标植物设置为焰球罂粟即可。\n\n警告：焰球罂粟高度敏感，如果周围温度超过28°C/82F，焰球罂粟即会自燃。当受到损坏时，它们还会泄漏一些苯基液体燃料与空气接触，从而点燃焰球罂粟。\n\n请确保您的种植园有良好的气候控制和防火性能，否则它很可能变成烧灼地狱！</CE_ObtainingPrometheum.helpText>
  
</LanguageData>